# Virtual environment
venv/                  ← don't upload packages to GitHub

# Environment variables
.env                   ← never upload your MySQL password

# Python cache
__pycache__/           ← auto-generated files, not needed
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Django
*.log                  ← log files, not needed
db.sqlite3             ← harmless, just ignore it
media/                 ← uploaded images go here, too large for GitHub

# VS Code
.vscode/               ← editor settings, personal to your machine

# Windows
Thumbs.db              ← Windows auto-generated, not needed
desktop.ini            ← Windows auto-generated, not needed